<h3>Html5</h3>

<p>Here are some html5 controls.</p>
<p>The controls are just standard {{#link-to 'controls.input'}}\{{zz-input}}{{/link-to}} tag with different <i>type</i> property.</p>

<div class="well line-example">
{{#zz-form model=model submit_button=false form_layout="horizontal"}}
    {{zz-input label="Email" property="email" type="email"}}
    {{zz-input label="Telephone" property="tel" type="tel"}}
    {{zz-input label="Range" property="range" type="range"}}
    {{zz-input label="Date" property="date" type="date"}}
    {{zz-input label="Time" property="time" type="time"}}
    {{zz-input label="Month" property="month" type="month"}}
    {{zz-input label="Week" property="week" type="week"}}
{{/zz-form}}
</div>